import jax
import jax.numpy as jnp

def generated_fn(x0, x1, x2):
    v0 = jnp.tanh(x2)
    v1 = jnp.subtract(x1, x2)
    v2 = jnp.multiply(x0, v1)
    v3 = jnp.multiply(x2, v1)
    v4 = jnp.cos(v3)
    v5 = jnp.exp(v2)
    v6 = jnp.exp(v2)
    v7 = jnp.maximum(v2, v6)
    v8 = jnp.exp(v0)
    v9 = jnp.maximum(v7, x0)
    return v9
